| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6012 — Recovery Inhibition (chaos)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: afe0db3d-6bff-5449-b0b6-dee3fb4a8f90"
